[normal]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;[bold]Clause 33 and paragraph [bold]6(3) and (4) of [bold]Schedule[bold] 14[bold]: schools - r[bold]eduction of burdens[bold] -[bold]p[bold]ublication[bold] of reports[bold]Powers conferred on
